Learning Aim: Create related Tables to demonstrate the power of relational databases
Prerequisites: User to have watched “Creating a basic task list” video&quot;
Introduction In this step of the guide we will build the engine of our CRM and in doing so start to introduce the concept of a relational database. We will do this as a practical example and you’ll see how agilebase makes this straight forward. We will be building a bigger system, but for the most part it’s simply reusing things we’ve already covered.
